topdressing
Homonym Number:  1
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:the fertilising of land with superphosphate, etc., in farming spread from machines or aeroplanes. -->see also TARANAKI TOPDRESSING the application of fertiliser to the surface of the soil (cf also AERIAL TOPDRESSING)
Origin: [none]
